OL,7,FOne of the UK's biggest energy firms
OL,8,Fhas halted the forced installation of
OL,9,Fprepayment meters in the UK's poorest
OL,10,Fhomes this Christmas, with pressure
OL,11,Fmounting on the Government to call an
OL,12,Furgent stop to the controversial
OL,13,Fpractice.
OL,15,FIt follows an investigation by i that
OL,16,Ffound that debt-collecting agents
OL,17,Facting on behalf of energy companies
OL,18,Fhad obtained nearly 500,000 warrants to
OL,19,Fenter properties since the last Covid
OL,20,Flockdown.
OL,3,COVO halts prepayment meters and debt
OL,4,Ccollection to ease pressure on
OL,5,Ccustomers over Christmas
